28
00:03:09,606 --> 00:03:10,899
Opo, ​​Kamahalan.

29
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:35,632
Tulungan Mo.

30
00:03:35,715 --> 00:03:36,925
Ano…

31
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:40,262
